  Description: 'You become trained in light armor. If you already were trained in
    light armor, you gain training in medium armor. If you were trained in both,
    you become trained in heavy armor. If you are at least 13th level, you become
    an expert in this armor type.



    Special You can select this feat more than
    once. Each time, you become trained in the next type of armor, as detailed above.'
